                        <h1>October 1, 2008</h1>                                  
                        Do you work better under deadline? Do you long for the day you can go back to school? Do you wish you could have all the market trends at your fingertips? Then this edition of CES Up to the Minute was crafted with you in mind.<BR><BR>But first, <A href="/register">register for free for the 2009 International CES</A>, January 8-11, Las Vegas, Nevada. It’s where to explore the digital landscape, more than 2,700 consumer electronics (CE) exhibits and 30 product categories from digital imaging to home networking.<BR>

